<h2>Why Bother Localizing Information Technology Products?</h2>
<h6 class="subheader"></h6>
</div>
<hr class="dotted" />
<div id="articleFullText" class="col1 floatLeft firstCol">
<span class="byline">
By Alex Tray
<br/>
Communications of the ACM,
February 2024,
Vol. 67 No. 2, Pages 6-7<br/>
10.1145/3638537<br/>
<a href="#comments">Comments</a>
